__de__ To tackle this problem , governments are using new tools to visualize the budget so it &apos;s more understandable to the public .
__de__ In this map from Moldova , the green color shows those districts that have low spending on schools but good educational outcomes , and the red color shows the opposite .
__de__ Tools like this help turn a shelf full of inscrutable documents into a publicly understandable visual , and what &apos;s exciting is that with this openness , there are today new opportunities for citizens to give feedback and engage with government .
