__ja__ This is the second shift : open aid .
__ja__ Recently , the World Bank opened its vault of data for public use , releasing 8,000 economic and social indicators for 200 countries over 50 years , and it launched a global competition to crowdsource innovative apps using this data .
__ja__ Development institutions today are also opening for public scrutiny the projects they finance .
